videos.description: Florida State turns a Pittsburgh miss into instant offense, as Rayquan Evans hits Patrick Williams for the slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams flushes home dunk for FSU) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: Williams flushes home dunk for FSU

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Xavier Johnson hustles back off a steal and cleans up a Trey McGowens' miss for two, plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson gets nifty putback to fall for Pitt) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: Johnson gets nifty putback to fall for Pitt

videos.description: Dominik Olejniczak's second block of the game ends up in the front row, as Xavier Johnson's challenge is denied by the FSU center.
videos.headline: Olejniczak sends Pittsburgh shot packing

videos.description: Malik Osborne carves up a Pittsburgh defender with a spin-move bank shot, plus the foul.
